WEBVTT

00:00.807 --> 00:02.382
<i>- Previously on</i> Bull...
- When we hear

00:02.407 --> 00:04.474
that one of our federal
employees and his family

00:04.476 --> 00:07.134
have been a victim
of arson, rape and murder,

00:07.159 --> 00:08.792
<i>we like to stick our nose in.</i>

00:08.794 --> 00:10.393
You, silver Explorer.

00:10.395 --> 00:12.996
<i>They haven't mentioned
it in the news reports,</i>

00:12.998 --> 00:14.230
<i>but Elliott is mute.</i>

00:14.232 --> 00:16.733
The government wants to execute you,

00:16.735 --> 00:19.169
and I would like to make sure
that doesn't happen.

00:19.171 --> 00:21.971
I think that you're in the
middle of some kind of crisis.

00:22.693 --> 00:24.498
Getting arrested, drinking too much,

00:24.523 --> 00:26.585
taking a death penalty case

00:26.610 --> 00:28.200
<i>'cause a guy gave you a handkerchief.</i>

00:28.202 --> 00:30.478
I haven't had a drink in 33 hours.

00:30.480 --> 00:32.171
<i>Seems like you're coming apart.</i>

00:32.171 --> 00:33.438
I'm fine.

00:33.440 --> 00:34.506
You know what? You're not.

00:34.508 --> 00:36.308
<i>Izzy's getting remarried.</i>

00:36.310 --> 00:37.576
Oh, my goodness.

00:37.578 --> 00:39.442
Can I tell you something?

00:39.444 --> 00:41.880
I don't think you're good alone, Jason.

00:41.882 --> 00:44.783
Professor Jameson, you failed me.

00:44.785 --> 00:47.519
Is it just that I work
for a trial scientist?

00:47.521 --> 00:48.754
I know he's innocent.

00:48.756 --> 00:49.654
No, you don't.

00:49.656 --> 00:51.022
- Did you do it?
<i>- You, you,</i>

00:51.024 --> 00:52.290
<i>you think he's innocent.</i>

00:52.292 --> 00:53.959
That's not the same thing,

00:53.961 --> 00:56.094
and more importantly, you don't know

00:56.096 --> 00:57.295
how to prove he's innocent.

00:57.297 --> 00:58.997
<i>Sorry to let everybody down.</i>

00:59.898 --> 01:02.534
But I think I need a drink.

01:10.811 --> 01:12.210
Hey, Izzy.

01:12.212 --> 01:14.146
There's a guy at the door for you.

01:15.783 --> 01:17.182
♪ They told me ♪

01:17.184 --> 01:19.551
♪ Be sensible ♪

01:19.553 --> 01:22.020
♪ With your new love ♪

01:22.022 --> 01:23.321
♪ Don't be fooled ♪

01:23.323 --> 01:27.492
♪ Thinking this is the last
you'll find... ♪

01:27.494 --> 01:28.894
Don't do this.

01:29.490 --> 01:31.200
No.

01:32.366 --> 01:34.299
Don't <i> you</i> do this.

01:34.301 --> 01:36.334
You can't just show up here

01:36.336 --> 01:37.636
at the last minute,

01:37.638 --> 01:38.937
and just expect me to...

01:38.939 --> 01:41.339
♪ And drive me slowly out of my mind ♪

01:41.341 --> 01:44.276
- ♪ Kiss me ♪
- ♪<i> Kiss me</i> ♪

01:44.278 --> 01:46.578
- ♪ Kiss me, and when you do ♪
- ♪<i> Kiss me</i> ♪

