♪ I know that you will miss me ♪

01:49.483 --> 01:51.583
- ♪<i> Miss me</i> ♪
- ♪ Miss me ♪

01:51.585 --> 01:54.719
♪ If we ever say "adieu" ♪

01:54.721 --> 01:56.788
♪ So kiss me ♪

01:56.790 --> 01:58.590
♪ Kiss me ♪

01:58.592 --> 02:00.225
♪ Make me tell you ♪

02:00.227 --> 02:04.362
♪ I'm in love with you ♪

02:04.364 --> 02:07.732
♪ <i>Ah, ah, ah, ah</i> ♪

02:07.734 --> 02:08.967
♪ <i>Kiss me</i> ♪

02:08.969 --> 02:10.836
- ♪ Kiss me ♪
- ♪<i> Kiss me...</i> ♪

02:10.838 --> 02:12.658
You were right.

02:14.041 --> 02:16.141
I'm no good alone.

02:16.143 --> 02:17.676
- ♪ Miss me ♪
- ♪<i> Miss me</i> ♪

02:17.678 --> 02:20.345
♪ If we ever say "adieu" ♪

02:20.347 --> 02:21.680
♪ So kiss me. ♪

02:23.383 --> 02:25.517
It is 6:45 in the morning.

02:25.519 --> 02:27.586
Time for all good trial
scientists to get up

02:27.588 --> 02:29.487
and at 'em so they can hear the verdict

02:29.489 --> 02:31.723
read this morning.

02:31.725 --> 02:35.760
Thank you.

02:35.762 --> 02:38.230
I, uh, I have no recollection
of calling you

02:38.232 --> 02:40.966
and asking you to bring me a new suit.

02:40.968 --> 02:43.568
It was at 3:17 this morning.

02:43.570 --> 02:45.804
I remember it vividly.

02:45.806 --> 02:46.905
Aha.

02:46.907 --> 02:48.777
Here's the thing,

02:49.409 --> 02:51.343
I know I've let you down.

02:51.345 --> 02:52.978
Some of the things,

02:52.980 --> 02:54.779
the behavioral things we discussed,

02:54.781 --> 02:57.214
things I did...

02:57.216 --> 03:00.914
I actually did get a handle on
them there for a couple of days.

03:03.834 --> 03:05.390
I'm sorry, Marissa.

03:05.392 --> 03:06.953
Will the defendant

03:06.978 --> 03:08.000
<i>please rise?</i>

03:12.199 --> 03:14.132
Has the jury reached a verdict?

03:14.134 --> 03:15.721
We have, Your Honor.

03:16.370 --> 03:18.103
We, the jury, find the defendant,

03:18.105 --> 03:19.704
Elliot Miles...

03:21.208 --> 03:24.271
guilty on two counts of capital murder.

